.3, 416.0, 1138.0, 432.7]}, {"text": "Thereafter  . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [662.8, 436.4, 1052.5, 453.5]}, {"text": "37", "bbox": [1121.3, 436.9, 1138.0, 453.5]}, {"text": "$3,225", "bbox": [1092.1, 463.9, 1138.0, 480.6]}, {"text": "5. RESTRUCTURING CHARGES", "bbox": [662.8, 541.1, 1008.4, 562.0]}, {"text": "The Company adopted a restructuring plan in 2001 and a", "bbox": [662.8, 578.1, 1124.2, 598.9]}, {"text": "second restructuring plan in 2002 as described below. In", "bbox": [662.8, 603.1, 1113.3, 623.9]}, {"text": "connection with these plans, the Company recorded", "bbox": [662.8, 628.1, 1079.5, 648.9]}, {"text": "restructuring charges of $28.9 million in 2001 (including a", "bbox": [662.8, 653.1, 1132.4, 674.0]}, {"text": "non-cash component of approximately $10.9 million) and", "bbox": [662.8, 678.1, 1123.3, 699.0]}, {"text": "$28.3 million in the fourth quarter of 2002 (including a", "bbox": [662.8, 703.1, 1110.1, 724.0]}, {"text": "non-cash component of approximately $2.5 million).", "bbox": [662.8, 728.1, 1085.4, 749.0]}, {"text": "The 2001 plan involved the following principal elements:", "bbox": [662.8, 765.6, 1117.8, 786.5]}, {"text": "(i) 31 underperforming branches were closed or consoli-", "bbox": [662.8, 790.7, 1107.5, 811.5]}, {"text": "dated with other locations; (ii) ﬁve administrative ofﬁces", "bbox": [662.8, 815.7, 1112.2, 836.5]}, {"text": "were closed or consolidated with other locations; (iii) the", "bbox": [662.8, 840.7, 1113.7, 861.5]}, {"text": "reduction of the Company’s workforce by 489 through the", "bbox": [662.8, 865.7, 1127.5, 886.5]}, {"text": "termination of branch and administrative personnel; and", "bbox": [662.8, 890.7, 1115.1, 911.5]}, {"text": "(iv) certain information technology hardware and software", "bbox": [662.8, 915.7, 1129.5, 936.5]}, {"text": "was no longer used.", "bbox": [662.8, 940.7, 818.4, 961.5]}, {"text": "The 2002 plan involved the following principal elements:", "bbox": [662.8, 978.2, 1120.1, 999.0]}, {"text": "(i) 40 underperforming branches and ﬁve administrative", "bbox": [662.8, 1003.2, 1112.0, 1024.1]}, {"text": "ofﬁces were closed or consolidated with other locations;", "bbox": [662.8, 1028.2, 1104.5, 1049.1]}, {"text": "(ii) the reduction of the Company’s workforce by 412", "bbox": [662.8, 1053.2, 1084.9, 1074.1]}, {"text": "through the termination of branch and administrative", "bbox": [662.8, 1078.2, 1092.9, 1099.1]}, {"text": "personnel; and (iii) a certain information technology", "bbox": [662.8, 1103.2, 1081.3, 1124.1]}, {"text": "project was abandoned.", "bbox": [662.8, 1128.3, 850.1, 1149.1]}, {"text": "The costs to vacate facilities primarily represent the pay-", "bbox": [662.8, 1165.8, 1110.3, 1186.6]}, {"text": "ment of obligations under leases offset by estimated sub-", "bbox": [662.8, 1190.8, 1111.4, 1211.6]}, {"text": "lease opportunities, the write-off of capital improvements", "bbox": [662.8, 1215.8, 1117.8, 1236.6]}, {"text": "made to such facilities and the write-off of related goodwill", "bbox": [662.8, 1240.8, 1131.5, 1261.6]}, {"text": "(only in 2001). The workforce reduction costs primarily", "bbox": [662.8, 1265.8, 1107.0, 1286.6]}, {"text": "represent severance. The information technology costs rep-", "bbox": [662.8, 1290.8, 1132.8, 1311.6]}, {"text": "resent the payment of obligations under equipment leases", "bbox": [662.8, 1315.8, 1120.4, 1336.6]}, {"text": "relating to the abandonment of certain information tech-", "bbox": [662.8, 1340.8, 1118.6, 1361.7]}, {"text": "nology projects.", "bbox": [662.8, 1365.8, 789.2, 1386.7]}, {"text": "The aggregate balance of the 2001 and 2002 charges was", "bbox": [662.8, 1403.3, 1114.1, 1424.2]}, {"text": "$17.3 million as of December 31, 2003. The Company esti-", "bbox": [662.8, 1428.3, 1135.7, 1449.2]}, {"text": "mates that approximately $6.8 million of this amount will", "bbox": [662.8, 1453.3, 1124.8, 1474.2]}, {"text": "be incurred by December 31, 2004 and approximately", "bbox": [662.8, 1478.4, 1095.4, 1499.2]}, {"text": "$10.5 million in future periods.", "bbox": [662.8, 1503.4, 912.7, 1524.2]}]}